### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  AEQUITAS — API Test Requests
###  How to use: click "Send Request" above any ### block
###  Make sure `make dev` is running first
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@ticker = AAPL

### ── Health ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Liveness check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Readiness check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/ready

### ── Market Data ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Ingest AAPL data — run this first
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/market-data/{{ticker}}/ingest?period=1y&interval=1d

### 2. Get stored OHLCV bars
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/market-data/{{ticker}}/bars?limit=5

### 3. Get company info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/market-data/{{ticker}}/info

### 4. Try a different ticker
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/market-data/SPY/ingest?period=6mo&interval=1d

### 5. Get SPY bars
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/market-data/SPY/bars?limit=10

### 6. Get more bars (full year)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/market-data/{{ticker}}/bars?limit=252
